rdida de dicho derecho}{\cs18\f0\fs28\up6\lang1034\langfe3082\langnp1034\insrsid15098319 \chftn {\footnote \pard\plain \qj \li0\ri-232\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin-232\lin0\itap0 \fs24\lang1034\langfe3082\cgrid\langnp1034\langfenp3082 {
